title: EFFICIENT WINTER RENTAL
posting_body: ['AVAILABLE SEPTEMBER 1, 2022:', 'This compact home is perfect for those not interested in sprawling spaces or large energy bills, and will appeal to a limited number of prospects!', 'YOU might be one of them!', ' Verizon FiOS HDTV and high speed internet are INCLUDED IN THE MONTHLY RENT.', ' The home is located in the friendly, quiet neighborhood of Rexhame Beach in Marshfield.', " Past tenants always rave about it's energy affordability!", '*', 'Availability: September 1, 2022 - May 31, 2023', '* Recently remodeled bathroom and Energy Star rated windows and doors installed.', '* Bedroom 1 has a full size bed, Bedroom 2 has a trundle bed.', '* Natural gas cooking stove and boiler for forced hot water heat.', '* Electric hot water heater.', '*', 'No smoking indoors.', '* NO PETS.', '* No groups or subletting allowed.', '* NOTE:  There are no clothes laundering facilities on the premises', '* Verification of employment/source of funds and references will be obtained', '* Initial payment of $ 3,850.00 (First/Last/Security Deposit of $ 800.00)', '* Owner pays HDTV, High Speed Internet, RE taxes, and water/sewer/trash municipal utilities', "* All other utilities, gas & electric, are tenant's responsibility.", 'This is a PTRT Managed Property.']
